OL,3,C'Capy-spa-ra': London Zoo opens new
OL,4,Cspa for a pair of Capybaras
OL,6,FA new spa - built exclusively for a
OL,7,Fpair of capybaras - has been unveiled
OL,8,Fby London Zoo.
OL,10,FBrother-sister duo, Gizmo and Kiwi,
OL,11,Fmoved to the Zoo in May 2025.
OL,13,FIt was only meant to be a temporary
OL,14,Fstay, but the keepers said they
OL,15,Fsettled in so well that a permanent
OL,16,Fhome was built.
OL,18,FThe rodents moved into their new
OL,19,Fluxury space - which features two
OL,20,Fpools, mud baths and climate control
OL,21,Fzones - on Tuesday.
