OL,3,C'Capy-spa-ra': London Zoo opens new
OL,4,Cspa for a pair of Capybaras
OL,6,FZookeeper Owen Shrewsbury said: "It's
OL,7,Fcalled Capy-spa-ra. They can have a
OL,8,Fnice day out, relax in their pond,
OL,9,Fhave a comfy day in their beds or
OL,10,Fwallow in their muddy wallow.
OL,12,F"We've got a good variety of terrain,
OL,13,Fwe have a big mound - under it they've
OL,14,Fgot a nice comfy bed, which has a
OL,15,Fheater for them.
