OL,3,C'Capy-spa-ra': London Zoo opens new
OL,4,Cspa for a pair of Capybaras
OL,6,F"We've got a wallow just by the
OL,7,Fwindows so in the summer time, when
OL,8,Fit's a bit warmer, they love to wallow
OL,9,Faround so they're all caked in mud.
OL,10,FThis is also to prevent parasites and
OL,11,Ftics that are typically in the wild."
OL,13,FThe Capybaras seem to be enjoying
OL,14,Ftheir new accommodation, but it's
OL,15,Foften hard to tell, according to Owen.
