OL,3,C'Capy-spa-ra': London Zoo opens new
OL,4,Cspa for a pair of Capybaras
OL,6,FHe said: "The capybara is completely
OL,7,Fexpressionless, you don't know what
OL,8,Fthey're thinking. Gizmo is a bit more
OL,9,Fsure of himself, he tends to push Kiwi
OL,10,Foff of her food sometimes but Kiwi
OL,11,Fkeeps herself to herself.
OL,13,F"She loves food, you can't get her
OL,14,Faway from it. She came out and was
OL,15,Fmunching on it straight away."
