OL,3,C'Capy-spa-ra': London Zoo opens new
OL,4,Cspa for a pair of Capybaras
OL,6,FCapybaras are the worlds largest
OL,7,Frodent and can grow to the size of a
OL,8,Fsmall dog. The zoo said they've grown
OL,9,Fpopular in recent years due to the
OL,10,Finternet - but the aim of the spa is
OL,11,Fto encourage the opposite.
OL,13,FThe spa will be open to visitors from
OL,14,FFriday 21 November with the aim of
OL,15,Feducating the public on why capybaras
OL,16,Fdon't make good pets.
